'''Y Prifardd''',<ref>http://www.websters-online-dictionary.org/translation/Welsh/prifardd{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/eisteddfod2008/sites/guide/history/pages/gorsedd.shtml BBC Guide to the Eisteddfod</ref> literally ''The Chief Bard'', is the [[Welsh language|Welsh]] title given to [[bard]]s who have won either the [[Chairing of the Bard|chair]] or the [[Crowning of the Bard|crown]] in the [[National Eisteddfod of Wales]].

